data.description: IMMACULATE 1-STORY ON A CUL-DE-SAC IN A FANTASTIC SOUTHWEST LOCATION. OPEN AND SPACIOUS FLOORPLAN THAT INCLUDES 4 BEDROOMS, 2 FULL BATHROOMS W/ TILE THROUGHOUT THE MAIN AREA OF THE HOME AND A SPACIOUS 2 CAR GARAGE. THE KITCHEN FEATURES AN OVERSIZED CENTER ISLAND WITH LOTS OF CABINETRY, PANTRY, STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES AND SOLID SURFACE COUNTERTOPS.  THERE IS A SLIDER LEADING TO THE REAR YARD WHICH WAS PROFESSIONALLY LANDSCAPED WITH ARTIFICIAL TURF, AN EXTENDED PATIO AREA AND LOW MAINTENANCE DESERT LANDSCAPING.  LOCATED WITHIN MINUTES OF SHOPPING, DINING AND FREEWAY ACCESS, THIS IS A STELLAR LOCATION.   ALL APPLIANCES CONVEY AND THEIR IS A CHOICE HOME WARRANTY THROUGH SEPTEMBER 2028 THAT WILL TRANSFER WITH THE HOUSE.
